data.description: Welcome home! Schedule your showing for this 3-bedroom, 1 large bath updated ranch home on Joliet's west side. 1300 sq ft of comfortable living. In 2017 this house was remodeled. Including stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, new sink & faucet, new drywall and all new wood laminate flooring and all new light fixtures. There is a one car attached garage with an attached utility/laundry room also good for storage. Master bedroom has 2 closets for ample space. All colors are neutral. Long driveway with huge fenced in yard. Easy access to all highways, shopping and entertainment. 5 minutes from downtown Joliet. We will give credit for new countertop  New windows 2017 and NEW ROOF Oct 2023 .  SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!  (Agent is related to seller)
